msgstr "Cop&y"

#. Translators: Message reported when attempting to delete a profile in the midst of a broadcast.
#: addon/appModules/splcommon/splconfui.py:202
msgid "An instant switch profile might be active or you are in the midst of a broadcast. If so, please press SPL Assistant, F12 to switch back to a previously active profile before opening broadcast profiles dialog to delete a profile."
